 效率大降。哪儿哪儿都不得劲，基本残废的 vim 模式，简直没法用。<br /><br />只好打开 Vim ，写一会再切回 Xcode 看看。太惨了", "last_modified": 1680662163, "replies": 40, "id": 929928}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1651385965", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1651385965", "title": "Android", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/android", "topics": 10206, "footer": "", "header": "来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。", "title_alternative": "Android", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965", "stars": 5332, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 39, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 582442, "username": "wwxwlw", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wwxwlw", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b9af/b27c/582442_mini.png?m=1680662975", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b9af/b27c/582442_normal.png?m=1680662975", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b9af/b27c/582442_large.png?m=1680662975", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b9af/b27c/582442_xlarge.png?m=1680662975", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b9af/b27c/582442_xlarge.png?m=1680662975", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b9af/b27c/582442_xlarge.png?m=1680662975", "created": 1653271340, "last_modified": 1680662975}, "last_reply_by": "lengyuqu", "last_touched": 1680707630, "title": "求推荐个手机😑", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/929937", "created": 1680663633, "deleted": 0, "content": "需求：可以刷外版系统或者有比较多活跃更新的类原生可以刷。\r\n三星外版是个不错的选择，但是，我目前用的港版，很多地方，登录三星账号，应用商店等很多都检测你的 SIM 卡，+86 和其他卡不一样，就算先插上其他卡，只要检测到启用了+86 卡就给你变回来。\r\n现在甚至三星键盘的翻译功能都“锁区”，不知道美版是不是这样。\r\n感谢解答。", "content_rendered": "需求：可以刷外版系统或者有比较多活跃更新的类原生可以刷。<br />三星外版是个不错的选择，但是，我目前用的港版，很多地方，登录三星账号，应用商店等很多都检测你的 SIM 卡，+86 和其他卡不一样，就算先插上其他卡，只要检测到启用了+86 卡就给你变回来。<br />现在甚至三星键盘的翻译功能都“